data.description: Completely renovated and move-in ready! Situated on a quiet lot just minutes from downtown Dover, this 3 Bedroom 2 Bathroom home offers countless improvements, quality upgrades and an oversized 32x24 detached garage! The main level boasts new chestnut flooring throughout, a spacious living room with tons of natural light & gorgeous kitchen. The custom kitchen showcases chestnut cabinetry, granite counter tops, custom back splash, stainless steel appliances & recessed lighting. The master bedroom features a spacious full bathroom with walk-in tile shower, dual sink vanity with granite countertops & large closet. Down the hall are three comfortable bedrooms and beautiful full bathroom surrounded in neutral tile & chestnut vanity. Additional features include large 16x16 deck, newer roof (2016), newer HVAC (2016) & a large detached garage ideal for contracting equipment, cars, boats - the options are endless! Schedule your tour today!
